name: Zooplankton biomass and abundance in Estonian territorial waters 1993-2016
description: Zooplankton dataset contains data on the species composition, biomass and abundance of meso- and merozooplankton groups. The data are gatheredduring the Estoniannational monitoring of coastal and open seainthe Baltic Sea. Samples are collectedvertically from three horizons 1)near-bottom to upper halocline layer, 2) halocline top layer to termocline top layer 3) termocline top layer to surface in accordancewith the Manual for Marine Monitoring in the COMBINE programme of HELCOM. The samples are analysed using microscopy. Biomass andabundance records are provided for such groups likeRotatoria, Copepoda, Cladoceraetc.
